org.openflow.protocol.table

Class OFFlowTableResource

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.openflow.protocol.OFMessage
      • org.openflow.protocol.table.OFFlowTableResource

  • public class OFFlowTableResource
extends OFMessage
    OFFlowTableResource describes the tables resource information of switch. It is sent from switch to controller.

    OFFlowTableResource
    {
    OFMessage header;

    int8 resourceType;
    int8 reserve[3];
    int32 counterNum;

    int32 meterNum;
    int32 groupNum;

    OFTableResource tableResources[OFTableType.MAX_TABLE_TYPE];
    } //size() = 8 + 16 + sizeof(OFTableResource) * OFTableType.MAX_TABLE_TYPE = 88

    Author:
    Song Jian (jack.songjian@huawei.com), Huawei Technologies Co., Ltd.
    See Also:
    OFTableResource
